channel.title: Dupe
channel.description: I will go straight to the point. I need some help with finding new ways to dupe. As you probably already know, you can change the amount of items with Cheat engine, but the value is not "true", It's fake If you know what I mean? Anyways, I have tried some things with this, but nothing have worked. So I just tried to [i]Examine[/i] the item, for example [i]Coins[/i]. So If I had 100m GP before and right clicked on [i]Examine[/i], It obviously stood [i]100000000 x Coins[/i]. And when I changed It to for example 200m GP and clicked on [i]Examine[/i], It stood [i]200000000 x Coins[/i]. So I'm wondering If there's a way there you can like, I don't know how to say It, but change the "fake" amount forever? I'm really sorry for my bad grammar, but I hope you know what I mean. And If this is not possible, is it anyone here who would like to help me finding a new way to dupe?
